### BetBlink API Test Requests

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3001/api/health

### Server Info
GET http://localhost:3001/api/info

### Register User
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "phoneNumber": "+1234567890",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "confirmPassword": "password123",
  "dateOfBirth": "1990-01-01",
  "address": {
    "street": "123 Main St",
    "city": "New York",
    "state": "NY",
    "postCode": "10001",
    "country": "United States"
  },
  "paymentMethod": {
    "type": "card",
    "cardNumber": "1234567890123456",
    "expiryDate": "12/25",
    "cvv": "123",
    "cardholderName": "John Doe"
  },
  "termsAccepted": true,
  "marketingConsent": false
}

### Login User
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Get User Profile (Replace with actual token)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/protected/profile
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### Get Dashboard Data (Replace with actual token)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/protected/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### Get Available Games
GET http://localhost:3001/api/games

### Get Game Rules
GET http://localhost:3001/api/games/1/rules

### Place a Bet (Replace with actual token)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/protected/games/1/bet
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "betAmount": 10,
  "betType": "heads"
}

### Refresh Token
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "YOUR_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE"
}
